import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Container = styled.div`
    height: 10%;
`;

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Wrapper>
        <List>
          <ListItem></ListItem>
          <ListItem></ListItem>
          <ListItem></ListItem>
          <ListItem></ListItem>
        </List>
        <Copyright></Copyright>
      </Wrapper>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Footer
